  "text": "The CSS style change to WebRender pipeline flows through 5 key C++ files: (1) **Style change notification**: `RestyleManager::PostRestyleEvent` in `layout/style/RestyleManager.cpp` queues restyle hints and change hints on elements. (2) **Frame style recomputation**: `RestyleManager::ProcessPendingRestyles` \u2192 `DoProcessPendingRestyles` runs Servo style traversal and calls `ProcessRestyledFrames` to apply nsChangeHints to frames, all in `RestyleManager.cpp`. (3) **Dirty-frame reflow scheduling**: `PresShell::FrameNeedsReflow` in `layout/base/PresShell.cpp` propagates dirty bits up the frame tree and adds roots to `mDirtyRoots`; `PresShell::DoReflow` performs the actual reflow. (4) **Display list construction**: `nsDisplayListBuilder` and display list item creation in `layout/painting/nsDisplayList.cpp`, invoked from `PresShell::PaintAndRequestComposite` \u2192 `PaintInternal`. (5) **WebRender layer update**: `WebRenderLayerManager::EndTransactionWithoutLayer` in `gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderLayerManager.cpp` drives `WebRenderCommandBuilder::CreateWebRenderCommandsFromDisplayList` in `gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderCommandBuilder.cpp` to convert display items into WebRender display list commands.",
